    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワのファン感謝祭について、改めて説明するぞ\n二人時代の曲を四人で歌う企画だけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm going to explain about the LizNoir fan festival again.\nIt's a project where the four of us will sing songs from the duo era…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0402042866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.774127094
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん……むむむ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Umm… Uuuuuum…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.774127094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "投票で『GIRI-GIRI borderless\nworld』をやることに決まったのは知ってるよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know that it was decided by vote to perform\nGIRI-GIRI borderless world'‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1756922881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.397233804
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "すやぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Zzzzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.397233804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……俺の話、聞いてるか？\nもしかして寝てるんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Are you listening to me?\nCould it be that you're sleeping…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.580136776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.947823139
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "しゃあーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shyaa!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.947823139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ、どうした急に？\n怒った野良猫のモノマネ……じゃなくて、起きたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa‚ what's with the sudden outburst?\nAn imitation of an angry stray cat… or did you just wake up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7921324968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.4978458522
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに顔を近づけてどうしたんですか？\nはっ、分かりました。こころに変な真似をしようと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you getting so close to my face?\nAh‚ I understand. You were trying to do something strange to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7333342552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.557822589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "違う。ファン感謝祭の打ち合わせ中なのに\nこころが居眠りしていたから、起こそうとしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I was trying to wake you up because\nyou were dozing off during the fan festival meeting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9084810178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "……すみません、ちょっと寝不足で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry‚ I haven't been getting enough sleep…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3900220353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.0843055526
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、別に怒ってはいないけど……\n寝不足なんてめずらしいな。どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ I'm not mad or anything…\nIt's unusual for you to be sleep-deprived. What's up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0191364527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "感謝祭でやる曲のことですけど\n昨日、ちょっと思うところがありまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's about the song for the festival.\nYesterday‚ I had some thoughts about it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6333312035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 73.14546173
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 73.14546173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "今日のレッスンもばっちりでした～\nファン感謝祭は、きっとすっごく盛り上がりますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's lesson went perfectly~\nThe fan festival is sure to be a huge hit~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7333312035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "あまりにも順調過ぎて怖いくらいです！\nこの分なら、こころ達のBIG4入りも時間の問題――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's going so smoothly‚ so it's almost scary!\nAt this rate‚ making us into the BIG4 is just a matter of time――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.9666645368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 88.7132173656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ、それどころか、もしかしてこころ達\nとっくにBIG4になっていたのでは……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Wait‚ could it be that\nwe've already made it into the BIG4…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2666645368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 95.5123170334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "……なんて冗談はさておき\n感謝祭でやる曲のおさらいをしないとですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Just kidding. Anyway‚\nWe need to review the song we're performing at the festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6333383243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリの映像を再生です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's replay the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix footage!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.965786278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 104.5953373231
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "『GIRI-GIRI\nborderless world』！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "'GIRI-GIRI\nborderless world'!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2000095685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.1394415972
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "懐かしいな。あの時、葵さんに怪我させちゃって……\n……なのに、それまでで一番のステージだった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's nostalgic. Back then‚ I injured Aoi-san…\n…And yet‚ it was the best stage we've ever had.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3333429019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.8273982165
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、凄いな。先輩達",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…They really are amazing‚ our seniors.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.8273982165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.5869643964
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.5869643964
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……つまり深夜まで映像を繰り返し観ていたから\n寝不足で、だから元気がないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So you stayed up late watching the footage over and over‚\nand that's why you're sleep-deprived and not feeling well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.557170987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "……こころ達は、大好きなリズノワの一員になれました\nでも、少しだけ……ほんの少～しだけ、思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…We became members of LizNoir‚ which we love so much.\nBut‚ just a little… just a tiny bit‚ I wonder.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8333373069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.6961626487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_07_01-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "あの時の『GIRI-GIRI』を\n今のこころ達は超えられるのかな……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can we surpass the 'GIRI-GIRI'\nfrom back then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.6333373069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
