      "text": "こころ達は、莉央さんと葵さんがあの曲を歌う姿に\nずーっと憧れて、ここまで来ましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've always admired Rio-san and Aoi-san singing that song‚\nand that's why we've come this far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.3666513124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
