      "text": "オーディションに落ちた時も、練習がきつい時も\nあの曲に励まされてきたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when we failed auditions or when practice was tough‚\nthat song encouraged us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.8999836284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
